{"tid":2406323,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】金世正開通全新官方SNS帳號！IG & Twitter & V LIVE & Youtube全都有~","createTime":"2021-02-13T06:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T18:03:37.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"320fa0c0a7bb69506a0ea09a4e2e7f8a7c26074e","tid":2406323,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T06:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_fcd6a3a0b8d5e1907fba4638cd9b9ab6/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-09/133617-896660.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_fcd6a3a0b8d5e1907fba4638cd9b9ab6%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-09%2F133617-896660.png&h=c2d5727c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以後可以在這些地方看到#金世正 的最新消息啦！<br />\n<br />\n金世正本月8日宣布開通了自己的Youtube、Instagram、Twitter、V LIVE和微博帳號，並上傳了第一支問候影片。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n金世正所屬的女團gu9dan在去年12月31日解散，之後以個人身份活動，之前都是通過gu9dan的SNS帳號更新動態，現在開始就將通過屬於自己的SNS跟大家分享近況啦！<br />\n<br />\n金世正在影片裡說：「終於！我的官方頻道開通了！以後會在官方頻道上傳很多很多趣的消息和故事，請大家多多訂閱和點讚！哇我一直都想講這句話來的~希望大家在我的頻道裡積累很多有趣的回憶！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HbQbdaEDyZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHbQbdaEDyZk&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ1YPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=a147929d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HbQbdaEDyZk</a><br />\n<br />\n世正還在個人IG裡分享了好幾張新的拍攝花絮照片，穿著碎花長裙，笑容依然那麼有活力：<br />\n<br />\n金世正全新的SNS賬號匯總都在這裡了，可以一一關注起來啦！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/0828_kimsejeong?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1358613035590447105%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F133617\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F0828_kimsejeong%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1358613035590447105%257Ctwgr%255E%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.koreastardaily.com%252Ftc%252Fnews%252F